metadata.name: Abandoned Building No. 2
metadata.description:
The REWORLD series by Roope Rainisto offers a contemplation of the intricacies of society through the interplay of bodies, identities, groups, events, and designed spaces. Rainisto's use of machine learning systems to generate images marks a turning point in our understanding of visual communication, providing a concentrated essence of visual thinking that reflects our technology-driven era. The world Rainisto creates is both familiar and unsettling, with fine yet flawed details that highlight how our perceptions are molded by visual representations. Through a unique perspective, Rainisto's images present figures and locales that challenge our imagination and venture into an elevated reality.



 Year: 2023

Edition: NFT 1 of 1
